1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Aaron Evans\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4974:\"<p>Add image shapes with the SiteOrigin Image Widget. Shapes initially available include Circle, Oval, Triangle, Square, Diamond, Rhombus, Parallelogram, Pentagon, and Hexagon with more to follow soon in the form of a SiteOrigin Premium Image Shape Addon.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_413454\" style=\"width: 2570px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-413454\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/image-shape-usage-live-editor-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1383\" class=\"size-full wp-image-413454\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/image-shape-usage-live-editor-scaled.jpg 2560w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/image-shape-usage-live-editor-300x162.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/image-shape-usage-live-editor-699x378.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/image-shape-usage-live-editor-768x415.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/image-shape-usage-live-editor-1536x830.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/image-shape-usage-live-editor-2048x1107.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/image-shape-usage-live-editor-1050x567.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/image-shape-usage-live-editor-313x169.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-413454\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A Circle applied to a link tree style profile photo.</p></div>\n<h3>Usage</h3>\n<p>The SiteOrigin Image Widget is part of the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/so-widgets-bundle/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle</a> and is ready to be used anywhere:</p>\n<p><strong>Page Builder:</strong><br />\nInsert widgets in Page Builder by SiteOrigin in either the Classic Editor or Page Builder Layout Block in the Block Editor.<br />\n<strong>Block Editor:</strong><br />\n100% Block Editor compatible. Insert widgets using the SiteOrigin Widgets Block featuring a live widget search form.<br />\n<strong>Theme and Plugin Widget Areas:</strong><br />\nInsert widgets into any theme or plugin widget area.</p>\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve inserted a SiteOrigin Image Widget and added your image, scroll down to the Image Shape heading to enable the section. There you&#8217;ll find the following settings.</p>\n<h4>Image Shape</h4>\n<div id=\"attachment_413457\" style=\"width: 2770px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-413457\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/so-image-shape-selection.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2760\" height=\"1434\" class=\"size-full wp-image-413457\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/so-image-shape-selection.png 2760w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/so-image-shape-selection-300x156.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/so-image-shape-selection-699x363.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/so-image-shape-selection-768x399.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/so-image-shape-selection-1536x798.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/so-image-shape-selection-2048x1064.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/so-image-shape-selection-1050x546.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/so-image-shape-selection-313x163.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2760px) 100vw, 2760px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-413457\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Select a shape from the available options.</p></div>\n<p><strong>Enable</strong><br />\nEnable to open the Image Shape settings section.</p>\n<p><strong>Image Shape</strong><br />\nSelect a shape from one of the available options.</p>\n<p>More shapes to come soon as part of a SiteOrigin Premium Image Shape Addon!</p>\n<p><strong>Repeat</strong><br />\nChoose from one of the following shape repeat options:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>No Repeat</li>\n<li>Repeat</li>\n<li>Repeat (No Clipping)</li>\n<li>Repeat Horizontally</li>\n<li>Repeat Vertically</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Size</strong><br />\nOptionally enter a size value for the shape. The size of your overall image can set by choosing a suitable size from the Image Size dropbox at the top of the widget settings. A Custom option is available.</p>\n<p><strong>Alignment</strong><br />\nChoose between aligning the shape on the Left, Center, or Right.</p>\n<h3>Useful Links</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/image-widget-documentation/\">SiteOrigin Image Widget Documentation</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks for reading. Please, let us know in the comments below if you have any questions.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/shapes-now-included-in-the-siteorigin-image-widget/\">Shapes Now Included in the SiteOrigin Image Widget</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:79:\"https://siteorigin.com/shapes-now-included-in-the-siteorigin-image-widget/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"Introducing the Page Background Addon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-the-page-background-addon/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-the-page-background-addon/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 24 Jul 2023 21:01:10 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=412542\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:554:\"<p>Introducing the SiteOrigin Premium Page Background. This powerful addon offers an exciting way to personalize your site\'s pages, providing you with the ability to add custom background images or color to individual or all pages and posts. This tool comes with an advanced feature to support high-pixel-density displays.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-the-page-background-addon/\">Introducing the Page Background Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Aaron Evans\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5726:\"<p>Introducing the SiteOrigin Premium Page Background. This powerful addon offers an exciting way to personalize your site&#8217;s pages, providing you with the ability to add custom background images or color to individual or all pages and posts. This tool comes with an advanced feature to support high-pixel-density displays.</p>\n<h4>Setting Your Custom Page Backgrounds</h4>\n<p>The Page Background Addon introduces a dual-level approach to setting background images on your website: global and page-specific settings:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Set a Global Page Background Image</strong>: Upload an image via the addon settings to have it displayed as the background across all pages of your website. This feature ensures a consistent background across your site.</li>\n<li><strong>Assign a Page Background Image per Page</strong>: For more personalization, you can assign a unique background image for each page. This feature allows you to match the background with the content or theme of each page.</li>\n</ol>\n<h4>Global Background Image Settings</h4>\n<p>Once activated, a global site background image can be added at <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin Premium Addons</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Page Background</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Settings</span></span>. </p>\n<div id=\"attachment_410118\" style=\"width: 772px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-410118\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/so-premium-page-background-global.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1484\" height=\"1088\" class=\"size-full wp-image-410118\" style=\"max-width: 742px\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/so-premium-page-background-global.png 1484w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/so-premium-page-background-global-300x220.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/so-premium-page-background-global-699x512.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/so-premium-page-background-global-768x563.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/so-premium-page-background-global-1050x770.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/so-premium-page-background-global-313x229.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-410118\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Add a global site background in the addon settings.</p></div>\n<p>The following settings are available:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Background Color: Choose a background color.</li>\n<li>Background Image: Select a background image.</li>\n<li>Background Image Display: Set how the background image is displayed (defaults to cover).</li>\n<li>Retina Background Image: Add a double-sized image for high-pixel-density displays.</li>\n<li>Selector: This is the selector used when applying a background. The default body is typically fine, but some themes may require a different selector.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The Retina Background Image requires the SiteOrigin Premium Retina Background Images Addon. If you don&#8217;t see the Retina Background Image field, go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span></span> and activate the Retina Background Images Addon.</p>\n<h4>Page-Specific Settings</h4>\n<p>The page-specific settings are similar to the global settings. You can set the background color, choose the background image, determine how the background image is displayed, and add a Retina background image.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_410170\" style=\"width: 726px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-410170\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/siteorigin-premium-page-background-settings.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1392\" height=\"847\" class=\"size-full wp-image-410170\" style=\"max-width: 696px\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/siteorigin-premium-page-background-settings.png 1392w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/siteorigin-premium-page-background-settings-300x183.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/siteorigin-premium-page-background-settings-699x425.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/siteorigin-premium-page-background-settings-768x467.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/siteorigin-premium-page-background-settings-1050x639.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/siteorigin-premium-page-background-settings-313x190.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1392px) 100vw, 1392px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-410170\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Add a page background by editing any page and locating the SiteOrigin Premium metabox below the content area.</p></div>\n<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/page-background/\">Page Background Addon Documentation</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">SiteOrigin Premium</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To conclude, the Page Background Addon provides an easy and efficient way to customize your webpages, offering greater flexibility and personalization. We can&#8217;t wait to see the amazing designs you&#8217;ll create!</p>\n<p>Stay tuned for more exciting updates from SiteOrigin!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-the-page-background-addon/\">Introducing the Page Background Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://siteorigin.com/introducing-the-page-background-addon/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:35:\"Announcing the Custom Palette Addon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:59:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-palette-addon/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:68:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-palette-addon/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 16 Jul 2023 20:03:10 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=412486\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:574:\"<p>We are thrilled to announce the release of the Custom Palette Addon released in SiteOrigin Premium version <code>1.43.0</code> on the 12th of April. Now, you can create a custom color palette for Page Builder and Widgets Bundle color settings, providing you with a more personalized and convenient color management system for your site design.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-palette-addon/\">Announcing the Custom Palette Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:11:\"Aaron Evans\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6257:\"<p>We are thrilled to announce the release of the Custom Palette Addon released in SiteOrigin Premium version <code>1.43.0</code> on the 12th of April. Now, you can create a custom color palette for Page Builder and Widgets Bundle color settings, providing you with a more personalized and convenient color management system for your site design.</p>\n<h3>Custom Palette Addon Overview</h3>\n<p>With the SiteOrigin Premium Custom Palette Addon, you can set and manage a color palette that&#8217;s tailored to your unique requirements. Whether it&#8217;s for Page Builder or Widgets Bundle, the Custom Palette Addon brings you the freedom to customize your color settings with ease.</p>\n<h3>Usage</h3>\n<p>To get started, visit <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin Premium Addons</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Custom Palette</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Settings</span></span> to manage your color settings. Here, you can add new colors to your palette and view your current selection.</p>\n<p>You can add a color to your palette by clicking the &#8216;Add&#8217; button and selecting your preferred color. If you need to remove a color, simply use the &#8216;Delete&#8217; icon next to the color. </p>\n<p>For existing colors in your palette, the icons on the right function as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Down Arrow: Opens the color in the color picker.</li>\n<li>Page Icon: Duplicates the color.</li>\n<li>Close Icon: Deletes the color.</li>\n<li>Click, hold, and drag to reorder your colors in the palette.</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_405255\" style=\"width: 1812px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-405255\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-full wp-image-405255\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-new-color.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1802\" height=\"932\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-new-color.png 1802w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-new-color-300x155.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-new-color-699x362.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-new-color-768x397.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-new-color-1536x794.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-new-color-1050x543.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-new-color-313x162.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1802px) 100vw, 1802px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-405255\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Use the color picker or enter an RGB value to create a new color option.</p></div>\n<p>In the below example, we&#8217;ll add a custom blue <code>#4d8ffb</code> as a new color option.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_405315\" style=\"width: 1784px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-405315\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-blue.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1774\" height=\"498\" class=\"size-full wp-image-405315\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-blue.png 1774w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-blue-300x84.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-blue-699x196.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-blue-768x216.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-blue-1536x431.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-blue-1050x295.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-blue-313x88.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1774px) 100vw, 1774px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-405315\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">In this example, we&#8217;ll add a custom blue <code>#4d8ffb</code> as a new color option.</p></div>\n<p>Once you&#8217;ve finished managing your color palette, click Save. Your color palette will be available in any Page Builder or Widgets Bundle setting that offers a color picker. In the below example we see our newly added color <code>#4d8ffb</code> available in the Page Builder Background Color picker.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_405320\" style=\"width: 2166px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-405320\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-color-option.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2156\" height=\"1360\" class=\"size-full wp-image-405320\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-color-option.jpg 2156w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-color-option-300x189.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-color-option-699x441.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-color-option-768x484.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-color-option-1536x969.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-color-option-2048x1292.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-color-option-1050x662.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/custom-color-option-313x197.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2156px) 100vw, 2156px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-405320\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Our newly added color #4d8ffb can be seen in the Page Builder color picker.</p></div>\n<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/custom-palette/\">SiteOrigin Premium Custom Palette Addon Documentation</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">Find Out More About SiteOrigin Premium</a>.</p>\n<p>Thank you for reading. Please feel free to let us know if you have any queries or requests. We&#8217;re sure you&#8217;re going to love the Custom Palette Addon as much as we do. Don&#8217;t hesitate to reach out if you have any questions, or if there&#8217;s something else you&#8217;d like to see. Enjoy crafting your color palette!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-palette-addon/\">Announcing the Custom Palette Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-palette-addon/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:3;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:47:\"Change Your Primary and Sticky Logo on Any Page\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://siteorigin.com/change-your-primary-and-sticky-logo-on-any-page/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:80:\"https://siteorigin.com/change-your-primary-and-sticky-logo-on-any-page/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Sun, 23 Apr 2023 19:12:59 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"Themes\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=405791\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:594:\"<p>After many suggestions and requests, we\'re excited to announce the SiteOrigin Logo Booster Addon! The Logo Booster Addon enhances your existing SiteOrigin theme logo functionality by allowing you to change your logo on any page. Your theme\'s sticky logo, displayed on scroll, can be changed globally for all pages or adjusted page-by-page.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/change-your-primary-and-sticky-logo-on-any-page/\">Change Your Primary and Sticky Logo on Any Page</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:8420:\"<p>After many suggestions and requests, we&#8217;re excited to announce the SiteOrigin Logo Booster Addon! If you&#8217;re using SiteOrigin Vantage, Corp, Unwind, or North, the Logo Booster Addon enhances your existing theme logo functionality by allowing you to change your logo on any page. Your theme&#8217;s sticky logo, displayed on scroll, can be changed globally for all pages or adjusted page-by-page. If you&#8217;re using WPML or Polylang to translate your site you can add a base and sticky logo per language.</p>\n<p>When might you want to change your theme&#8217;s primary logo? Product or service landing pages or perhaps when you&#8217;re using the Corp Header Overlap feature seen on the <a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/\">demo home page</a> are just a couple of examples that come to mind. Moving on to the sticky logo, usually, the site header is smaller on scroll; an alternate logo might be appropriate to use the space best available. Similarly, adjusting the sticky logo for the page in question might be helpful if the primary logo has been changed for a specific page.</p>\n<h3>Requirements</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">SiteOrigin Premium Plugin</a></li>\n<li>One of the following SiteOrigin themes: <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/vantage/\">Vantage</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/siteorigin-corp/\">Corp</a>, <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/siteorigin-unwind\">Unwind</a>, or <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/siteorigin-north/\">North</a>.</li>\n<li>Optional: <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/\">SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle Plugin</a></li>\n<li>Optional: <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/page-builder/\">Page Builder by SiteOrigin Plugin</a></li>\n<li>Optional: <a href=\"https://wpml.org/?aid=88702&#038;affiliate_key=V5z6Km6VwAK0\">WPML</a> for website languange translation.\n<li>Optional: <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/polylang/\">Polylang</a> for website languange translation.\n</ul>\n<p>To get started, head over to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span></span> and activate the Logo Booster Addon.</p>\n<h3>How to Use the Logo Booster Addon</h3>\n<p>Once your regular and Retina logo has been added to your theme, you can use the Logo Booster Addon to do the following:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Change the global sticky logo.</li>\n<li>Change the logo on any page.</li>\n<li>Change the sticky logo on any page.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To add a global sticky logo, go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Logo Booster</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Settings</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Global Sticky Logo</span></span>. Click the Choose Media button to add a global sticky logo.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_401939\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-401939\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"size-large wp-image-401939\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/logo-booster-global-settings-1-699x354.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"354\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/logo-booster-global-settings-1-699x354.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/logo-booster-global-settings-1-300x152.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/logo-booster-global-settings-1-768x389.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/logo-booster-global-settings-1-1536x778.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/logo-booster-global-settings-1-1050x532.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/logo-booster-global-settings-1-313x159.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/03/logo-booster-global-settings-1.png 1666w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-401939\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Add a global sticky logo from SiteOrigin &gt; Premium Addons &gt; Logo Booster: Settings</p></div>\n<p>If you&#8217;re using <a href=\"https://wpml.org/?aid=88702&#038;affiliate_key=V5z6Km6VwAK0\">WPML</a> or <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/polylang/\">Polylang</a> to translate your site you&#8217;ll find a base and sticky logo setting per languange available at <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Logo Booster</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Settings</span></span>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_408221\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-408221\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-additional-languages-699x237.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"237\" class=\"size-large wp-image-408221\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-additional-languages-699x237.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-additional-languages-300x102.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-additional-languages-768x260.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-additional-languages-1536x520.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-additional-languages-2048x694.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-additional-languages-1050x356.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-additional-languages-313x106.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-408221\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The above website has been translated into English and Portuguese. A base and sticky logo setting is added per additional site language.</p></div>\n<p>To add a page-specific regular or sticky logo, go to Pages and edit your chosen page. Locate the Logo Booster metabox below the main page content area. A Logo and Sticky Logo setting is available. Click the Add Media button to add your logos as required. It isn&#8217;t necessary to add both a regular and sticky logo. Either setting can be used independently.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_408200\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-408200\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-408200 size-large\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-metabox-699x293.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"293\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-metabox-699x293.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-metabox-300x126.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-metabox-768x322.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-metabox-1050x440.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-metabox-313x131.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/logo-booster-metabox.png 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-408200\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">A Logo and Sticky Logo setting is available on each page below the main page content area.</p></div>\n<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/theme-addons/logo-booster/\">Logo Booster Addon Documentation</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">Find Out More About SiteOrigin Premium</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks for reading. Please, let us know if you have any queries or requests. We hope you find the Logo Booster Addon useful.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/change-your-primary-and-sticky-logo-on-any-page/\">Change Your Primary and Sticky Logo on Any Page</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"https://siteorigin.com/change-your-primary-and-sticky-logo-on-any-page/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"Add Multiple Google Map Marker Addresses at Once\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:72:\"https://siteorigin.com/add-multiple-google-map-marker-addresses-at-once/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"https://siteorigin.com/add-multiple-google-map-marker-addresses-at-once/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 13 Apr 2023 20:14:26 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=404900\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:518:\"<p>Adding multiple markers to your Google Maps Widget can be a time-consuming task, but with the Bulk Addresses Addon, you can easily enter multiple addresses into a single field, and voila! Each address will create a marker on the map, saving you time and effort.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/add-multiple-google-map-marker-addresses-at-once/\">Add Multiple Google Map Marker Addresses at Once</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4688:\"<p>Looking to save some valuable time when adding multiple markers to your Google Maps Widget? We have some exciting news for you! Introducing the Bulk Addresses Addon, the newest member of the SiteOrigin Premium addon family.</p>\n<p>Adding multiple markers to your Google Maps Widget can be a time-consuming task, but with the Bulk Addresses Addon, you can easily enter multiple addresses into a single field, and voila! Each address will create a marker on the map, saving you time and effort.</p>\n<h3>Usage</h3>\n<div id=\"attachment_404641\" style=\"width: 310px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-404641\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-404641 size-medium\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-addresses-300x163.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"300\" height=\"163\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-addresses-300x163.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-addresses-313x170.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/add-addresses.png 640w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-404641\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Marker addresses can be added one per line. It&#8217;s not a problem if an address uses multiple lines. Press Enter before adding a new marker address.</p></div>\n<p>Click the Add Addresses button when you&#8217;re ready to add your map markers.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_404644\" style=\"width: 2124px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-404644\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/addressess-added.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2114\" height=\"413\" class=\"size-full wp-image-404644\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/addressess-added.png 2114w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/addressess-added-300x59.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/addressess-added-699x137.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/addressess-added-768x150.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/addressess-added-1536x300.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/addressess-added-2048x400.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/addressess-added-1050x205.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/addressess-added-313x61.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2114px) 100vw, 2114px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-404644\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Click the Add Addresses button to add your map markers.</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_405067\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-405067\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/map-markers-699x294.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"294\" class=\"size-large wp-image-405067\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/map-markers-699x294.jpg 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/map-markers-300x126.jpg 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/map-markers-768x323.jpg 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/map-markers-1536x647.jpg 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/map-markers-2048x862.jpg 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/map-markers-1050x442.jpg 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/map-markers-313x132.jpg 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-405067\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Map markers can be displayed in their default form or customized using the widget options.</p></div>\n<h3>Speed Up Your Workflow</h3>\n<p>We understand that the Bulk Addresses Addon may seem like a small addition, but it can make a big impact on your workflow. It&#8217;s a perfect example of how even the smallest addon can make a big difference.</p>\n<p>If you&#8217;re a SiteOrigin Premium user, be sure to check out the Bulk Addresses Addon and give it a try. You&#8217;ll find that it&#8217;s a lifesaver when you need to add multiple markers. Happy mapping!</p>\n<p>For more information, you can visit our <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/google-maps-widget/\">SiteOrigin Google Maps Widget Documentation</a> and our <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/bulk-addresses/\">SiteOrigin Premium Bulk Addresses Addon Documentation</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/add-multiple-google-map-marker-addresses-at-once/\">Add Multiple Google Map Marker Addresses at Once</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://siteorigin.com/add-multiple-google-map-marker-addresses-at-once/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:45:\"Announcing the Retina Background Images Addon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-retina-background-images-addon/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:78:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-retina-background-images-addon/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Mon, 20 Mar 2023 21:20:09 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=402495\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:507:\"<p>We are excited to announce the release of our latest addon for SiteOrigin Premium: Retina Background Images! This new addon enhances your website\'s visuals by adding support for high-pixel-density displays, ensuring your site looks stunning on all devices.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-retina-background-images-addon/\">Announcing the Retina Background Images Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9205:\"<p>We are excited to announce the release of our latest addon for SiteOrigin Premium: Retina Background Images! This new addon enhances your website&#8217;s visuals by adding support for high-pixel-density displays, ensuring your site looks stunning on all devices.</p>\n<h3>What Does the Retina Background Images Addon Do?</h3>\n<p>The Retina Background Images Addon allows you to add Retina-ready background images for widgets, cells, and rows on your Page Builder powered pages. This ensures that your background images look sharp and clear on high-resolution displays, like those found on Retina devices.</p>\n<h3>Usage</h3>\n<p>Go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Retina Background Images</span></span> to activate the addon. Retina background images can be added to rows, cells, or widgets.</p>\n<p>The default Background Image field is designed for regular screens with lower-resolution displays. For utilizing a high-resolution image on devices with sharper displays, upload it to the Retina Background Image field. Web browsers will automatically choose the suitable image according to the display in use, helping to avoid a discernible decline in image quality on high-resolution screens.</p>\n<h4>Rows</h4>\n<p>To add a Page Builder row Retina background image, edit any Page Builder layout. Edit a row by clicking the wrench icon on the right and then opening the Design section.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_394899\" style=\"width: 1852px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-394899\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-row.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1842\" height=\"556\" class=\"size-full wp-image-394899\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-row.png 1842w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-row-300x91.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-row-699x211.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-row-768x232.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-row-1536x464.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-row-1050x317.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-row-313x94.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1842px) 100vw, 1842px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-394899\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Click the wrench icon to edit a row. Open the Design settings section.</p></div>\n<p>Add a row background image to be used on standard-pixel-density displays using the Background Image field. Either use the Select Image button to browse your Media Library or the External URL field to use an image hosted on another domain. Once a background image has been added, the Retina Background Image setting will be displayed. Click the Select Image button or use the External URL field to add your high-pixel-density display background image. The standard-pixel-density display background image is used as a base size during the Retina background image output. As a result, both images are required.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_394900\" style=\"width: 317px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-394900\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/retina-background-image-setting-307x699.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"307\" height=\"699\" class=\"size-large wp-image-394900\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/retina-background-image-setting-307x699.png 307w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/retina-background-image-setting-132x300.png 132w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/retina-background-image-setting-461x1050.png 461w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/retina-background-image-setting-313x712.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/retina-background-image-setting.png 552w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 307px) 100vw, 307px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-394900\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The Retina Background Image setting will be displayed once a standard display Background Image has been added.</p></div>\n<h4>Cells</h4>\n<p>To add a Page Builder cell Retina background image, edit any Page Builder layout. Edit a row by clicking the wrench icon on the right. Click on the cell you&#8217;d like to edit; a corresponding Cell Styles section will appear. Open the Design section to add the Background and Retina Background Images.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_395000\" style=\"width: 2770px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-395000\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/page-builder-cell-styles.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2760\" height=\"1480\" class=\"size-full wp-image-395000\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/page-builder-cell-styles.png 2760w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/page-builder-cell-styles-300x161.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/page-builder-cell-styles-699x375.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/page-builder-cell-styles-768x412.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/page-builder-cell-styles-1536x824.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/page-builder-cell-styles-2048x1098.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/page-builder-cell-styles-1050x563.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/page-builder-cell-styles-313x168.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2760px) 100vw, 2760px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-395000\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Click on the cell you&#8217;d like to edit; a corresponding Cell Styles section will appear.</p></div>\n<h4>Widgets</h4>\n<p>To add a Page Builder widget Retina background image, edit any Page Builder layout. Hover over your chosen widget and click to edit. Open the <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Widget Styles</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Design</span></span> section on the right to add a Background and Retina Background Image.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_395002\" style=\"width: 1792px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-395002\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-widget.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1782\" height=\"124\" class=\"size-full wp-image-395002\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-widget.png 1782w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-widget-300x21.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-widget-699x49.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-widget-768x53.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-widget-1536x107.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-widget-1050x73.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/edit-widget-313x22.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1782px) 100vw, 1782px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-395002\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Hover over your chosen widget and click to edit.</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_395003\" style=\"width: 2770px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-395003\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/widget-styles.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2760\" height=\"1352\" class=\"size-full wp-image-395003\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/widget-styles.png 2760w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/widget-styles-300x147.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/widget-styles-699x342.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/widget-styles-768x376.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/widget-styles-1536x752.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/widget-styles-2048x1003.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/widget-styles-1050x514.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/01/widget-styles-313x153.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2760px) 100vw, 2760px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-395003\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Open the Widget Styles > Design section on the right to add a Background and Retina Background Image.</p></div>\n<h4>Upgrade Your Site&#8217;s Visuals Today</h4>\n<p>The Retina Background Images Addon is a fantastic addition to the SiteOrigin Premium plugin suite. Enhance your website&#8217;s visuals and make sure it looks stunning on high-resolution displays with this easy-to-use addon. Upgrade your <a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium\">SiteOrigin Premium plugin</a> today to enjoy the benefits of Retina Background Images!</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-retina-background-images-addon/\">Announcing the Retina Background Images Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:74:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-retina-background-images-addon/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"2\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:6;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:38:\"Announcing the Custom Row Colors Addon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:62:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-row-colors-addon/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:71:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-row-colors-addon/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 27 Dec 2022 18:21:23 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=394336\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:503:\"<p>Organize your Page Builder rows with custom background colors. Page Builder offers five admin row background colors to help visually organize your pages. The Custom Row Colors Addon lets you add, remove, order, and name your Page Builder admin row background colors.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-row-colors-addon/\">Announcing the Custom Row Colors Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7422:\"<p>Organize your Page Builder rows with custom background colors. Page Builder offers five admin row background colors to help visually organize your pages. The Custom Row Colors Addon lets you add, remove, order, and name your Page Builder admin row background colors.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_394337\" style=\"width: 1856px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-394337\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1846\" height=\"1158\" class=\"size-full wp-image-394337\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors.png 1846w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-300x188.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-699x438.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-768x482.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-1536x964.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-1050x659.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/page-builder-admin-row-bg-colors-313x196.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1846px) 100vw, 1846px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-394337\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Page Builder offers five admin row background colors to help visually organize your pages.</p></div>\n<h3>Usage</h3>\n<p>Go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Premium Addons</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Custom Row Colors</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Settings</span></span> to manage your Page Builder admin row background colors.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_394239\" style=\"width: 2740px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-394239\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2730\" height=\"940\" class=\"size-full wp-image-394239\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors.png 2730w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-300x103.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-699x241.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-768x264.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-1536x529.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-2048x705.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-1050x362.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-pb-row-background-colors-313x108.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2730px) 100vw, 2730px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-394239\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Manage Page Builder row background colors from SiteOrigin > Premium Addons > Custom Row Colors.</p></div>\n<p>Click the Add button to add a new row background color. For existing row background colors, the icons on the right function as follows:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Down Arrow: Opens the row background color.</li>\n<li>Page Icon: Duplicates the row background color.</li>\n<li>Close Icon: Deletes the background row color.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Click, hold, and drag to reorder your row background colors.</p>\n<p>The following fields are available when adding a new row background color:</p>\n<p><strong>Name</strong><br />\nAdd a name for the row background color. This is a required field.</p>\n<p><strong>Active Color</strong><br />\nSelect the row background active color.</p>\n<p><strong>Cell Divider</strong><br />\nSelect the row background cell divider color.</p>\n<p><strong>Cell Divider Hover</strong><br />\nSelect the row background cell divider hover color.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_394246\" style=\"width: 2740px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-394246\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"2730\" height=\"1480\" class=\"size-full wp-image-394246\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color.png 2730w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-300x163.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-699x379.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-768x416.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-1536x833.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-2048x1110.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-1050x569.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/manage-custom-row-bg-color-313x170.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2730px) 100vw, 2730px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-394246\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The above fields are available when adding a new row background color.</p></div>\n<h3>Applying Row Background Colors</h3>\n<p>Edit any page using Page Builder or a Page Builder Layout Block to apply row background colors. Click the wrench icon to edit a row. Select the color swatch you&#8217;d like to apply as the row background color.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_394243\" style=\"width: 1940px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-394243\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1930\" height=\"841\" class=\"size-full wp-image-394243\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch.png 1930w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-300x131.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-699x305.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-768x335.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-1536x669.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-1050x458.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/select-a-swatch-313x136.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1930px) 100vw, 1930px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-394243\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Click the wrench icon to edit a row and select a background color swatch.</p></div>\n<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/custom-row-colors/\">Custom Row Colors Addon Documentation</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium\">Find Out More About Siteorigin Premium</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks for reading. Please, let us know if you have any queries or requests. We hope you find the Custom Row Colors Addon useful.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-row-colors-addon/\">Announcing the Custom Row Colors Addon</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:67:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-custom-row-colors-addon/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:7;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:37:\"Announcing the SiteOrigin Blog Widget\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-siteorigin-blog-widget/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:70:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-siteorigin-blog-widget/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Tue, 27 Sep 2022 20:48:43 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=382552\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:488:\"<p>We\'re excited to announce the SiteOrigin Blog Widget and SiteOrigin Premium Blog Addon. Display your blog posts in a list or grid. Choose from one of the following beautifully designed templates; Standard, Grid, Offset, Alternate, Masonry, or Portfolio.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-siteorigin-blog-widget/\">Announcing the SiteOrigin Blog Widget</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4293:\"<p>We&#8217;re excited to announce the SiteOrigin Blog Widget and SiteOrigin Premium Blog Addon. Display your blog posts in a list or grid. Choose from one of the following beautifully designed templates; Standard, Grid, Offset, Alternate, Masonry, or Portfolio.</p>\n<p>The Blog Widget is ready to be used anywhere:</p>\n<p><strong>Page Builder:</strong> Insert widgets in Page Builder by SiteOrigin in either the Classic Editor or Page Builder Layout Block in the Block Editor.<br />\n<strong>Block Editor:</strong> 100% Block Editor compatible. Insert widgets using the SiteOrigin Widgets Block featuring a live widget search form.<br />\n<strong>Theme and Plugin Widget Areas:</strong> Insert widgets into any theme or plugin widget area.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_385487\" style=\"width: 1900px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-385487\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1890\" height=\"1392\" class=\"size-full wp-image-385487\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings.png 1890w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-300x221.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-699x515.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-768x566.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-1536x1131.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-1050x773.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/09/so-blog-grid-settings-313x231.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1890px) 100vw, 1890px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-385487\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">The available Settings and Design options change based on the template selected.</p></div>\n<h4>Blog Widget Templates Demo Links</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-standard-template/\">Standard</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-grid-template/\">Grid</a></a>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-offset-template/\">Offset</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-alternate-template/\">Alternate</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-masonry-template/\">Masonry</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/blog-widget-portfolio-template/\">Portfolio</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>SiteOrigin Premium Blog Addon</h3>\n<p>The Blog Addon introduces the following settings to the Blog Widget:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Excerpt Trim Indicator: Customize the excerpt trim indicator. Defaults to <code>...</code></li>\n<li>Post Read More Link Text: Customize the Post Excerpt or the Full Post Content read more text.</li>\n<li>Post Date Format: Select the post meta date format.</li>\n<li>Pagination: Adds three additional pagination styles, Previous &#8211; Next, Load More, and Infinite Scrolling.</li>\n<li>Pagination Page Reload: Select the pagination page reload style. Choose between Standard and Ajax.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>More settings and features will be added in the future as we receive feedback and requests from our users.</p>\n<h4>SiteOrigin Premium Blog Addon Pagination Demos</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/blog-prev-next/\">Previous &#8211; Next Pagination with Ajax Page Reloading</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/blog-load-more/\">Load More Pagination with Ajax Reloading</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/blog-infinite-scrolling/\">Infinite Scrolling Pagination (with Ajax Reloading)</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Useful Links</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/blog-widget/\">Blog Widget Documentation</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/blog/\">Premium Blog Addon Documentation</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks for reading. Please, let us know if you have any queries or requests. We hope you find the Blog Widget useful.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-siteorigin-blog-widget/\">Announcing the SiteOrigin Blog Widget</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:66:\"https://siteorigin.com/announcing-the-siteorigin-blog-widget/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:2:\"14\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:8;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:76:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Stop Spam With Really Simple CAPTCHA\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:60:\"https://siteorigin.com/stop-spam-with-really-simple-captcha/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:69:\"https://siteorigin.com/stop-spam-with-really-simple-captcha/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Fri, 24 Jun 2022 18:28:33 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"Announcements\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"Plugins\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:32:\"https://siteorigin.com/?p=373568\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:686:\"<p>The <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/so-widgets-bundle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SiteOrigin Contact Form Widget</a> now includes support for the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/really-simple-captcha/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Really Simple CAPTCHA</a> plugin authored by Takayuki Miyoshi. If you\'re a user running a website in Germany, you\'ll be happy to know that you can stop contact form spam while complying with the DSGVO.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/stop-spam-with-really-simple-captcha/\">Stop Spam With Really Simple CAPTCHA</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:4437:\"<p>The <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/so-widgets-bundle\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SiteOrigin Contact Form Widget</a> now includes support for the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/really-simple-captcha/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Really Simple CAPTCHA</a> plugin authored by Takayuki Miyoshi. If you&#8217;re a user running a website in Germany, you&#8217;ll be happy to know that you can stop contact form spam while complying with the DSGVO. If you&#8217;d like to add a CAPTCHA to your SiteOrigin Contact Form or if you&#8217;d like to switch from Google&#8217;s reCAPTCHA service, read on to find out more.</p>\n<p>1. To get started, make sure you have the SiteOrigin Widgets Bundle plugin installed and activated. The Widgets Bundle can be installed from <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Plugins</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Add New</span></span>.</p>\n<p>2. Once activated, go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Plugins</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">SiteOrigin Widgets</span></span> to activate the Contact Form Widget.</p>\n<p>3. Insert or edit an existing Contact Form Widget. The Contact Form Widget is ready to be inserted anywhere.</p>\n<p><strong>Page Builder:</strong> Insert widgets in Page Builder by SiteOrigin in either the Classic Editor or Page Builder Layout Block in the Block Editor.<br />\n<strong>Block Editor:</strong> 100% Block Editor compatible. Insert widgets using the SiteOrigin Widgets Block featuring a live widget search form.<br />\n<strong>Theme and Plugin Widget Areas:</strong> Insert widgets into any theme or plugin widget area.</p>\n<p>4. Once editing your Contact Form Widget, go to <span class=\"adminized-section\"><span class=\"adminized-part\">Spam Protection</span><span class=\"adminized-arrow icon-arrow-right\"></span><span class=\"adminized-part\">Really Simple CAPTCHA</span></span> and enable the <strong>Add Really Simple CAPTCHA</strong> setting. The following additional settings are available:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Background Color</li>\n<li>Text Color</li>\n</ul>\n<div id=\"attachment_373611\" style=\"width: 1952px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-373611\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1942\" height=\"1294\" class=\"size-full wp-image-373611\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha.png 1942w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-300x200.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-699x466.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-768x512.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-1536x1023.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-1050x700.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-313x209.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-720x480.png 720w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/widgets-bundle-spam-protection-really-simple-captcha-272x182.png 272w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1942px) 100vw, 1942px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-373611\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Open the Spam Protection settings section to enable the Really Simple CAPTCHA.</p></div>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/corp/contact/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">View a Demo</a>.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/widgets-bundle/contact-form-widget/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">SiteOrigin Contact Form Widget Documentation</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Thanks for reading. If you have any queries or requests, please, let us know in the comments below.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/stop-spam-with-really-simple-captcha/\">Stop Spam With Really Simple CAPTCHA</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:65:\"https://siteorigin.com/stop-spam-with-really-simple-captcha/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"x