:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:619:\"<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/?featured_addon=plugin/anchor-id\">SiteOrigin Premium</a> <code>1.32.0</code> introduces the Anchor ID Addon. Link users directly to SiteOrigin Slides, Tabs, and Accordion panels. Once enabled, a unique anchor ID is added to the page URL corresponding to each SiteOrigin Slide, Tab, and Accordion panel.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/link-to-directly-to-slides-tabs-and-accordion-panels/\">Link to Directly to Slides, Tabs, and Accordion Panels</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Andrew Misplon\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:3686:\"<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/?featured_addon=plugin/anchor-id\">SiteOrigin Premium</a> <code>1.32.0</code> introduces the Anchor ID Addon. Link users directly to SiteOrigin Slides, Tabs, and Accordion panels. Once enabled, a unique anchor ID is added to the page URL corresponding to each SiteOrigin Slide, Tab, and Accordion panel. The unique anchor allows for direct linking to specific content within each widget.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_370222\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-370222\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-699x599.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"599\" class=\"size-large wp-image-370222\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-699x599.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-300x257.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-768x658.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-1050x900.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor-313x268.png 313w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/set-custom-anchor.png 1244w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-370222\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Enable the Anchor setting and enter a custom ID.</p></div>\n<p>The following widgets are supported:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Accordion</li>\n<li>Hero</li>\n<li>Layout Slider</li>\n<li>Slider</li>\n<li>Tabs</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You&#8217;ll find the Anchor ID valuable if you&#8217;ve used any of the above widgets to condense content. Frequently Asked Questions or a Table of Contents are two possible use cases.</p>\n<p><strong>Link Demo</strong><br />\nThe following URL will link to the third Accordion panel <a href=\"https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/anchor-id/#accordion-panel-three\">https://demo.siteorigin.com/premium/anchor-id/#accordion-panel-three</a>.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_370230\" style=\"width: 709px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-370230\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-699x254.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"699\" height=\"254\" class=\"size-large wp-image-370230\" srcset=\"https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-699x254.png 699w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-300x109.png 300w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-768x279.png 768w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-1536x557.png 1536w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-2048x743.png 2048w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-1050x381.png 1050w, https://siteorigin.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/link-panel-three-313x114.png 313w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 699px) 100vw, 699px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-370230\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Our demo link opens the third Accordion panel.</p></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/premium-documentation/plugin-addons/anchor-id/\">View the Addon Documentation</a>.<br />\n<a href=\"https://siteorigin.com/downloads/premium/\">Find Out More About SiteOrigin Premium</a>.</p>\n<p>Thanks for reading. If you have any queries or requests, please, don&#8217;t hesitate to reach out.</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com/link-to-directly-to-slides-tabs-and-accordion-panels/\">Link to Directly to Slides, Tabs, and Accordion Panels</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://siteorigin.com\">SiteOrigin</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:81:\"https://siteorigin.com/link-to-directly-to-slides-tabs-and-accordion-panels/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"4\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}s:27:\"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom\";a:1:{s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:4:\"href\";s:28:\"https://siteorigin.com/feed/\";s:3:\"rel\";s:4:\"self\";s:4:\"type\";s:19:\"application/rss+xml\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:44:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/\";a:2:{s:12:\"updatePeriod\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"\n	hourly	\";s:7:\"at